Tehachapi.title: Tehachapi
Tehachapi.byline: Tehachapi is a city in Kern County, California in a valley within the Tehachapi Mountains which separate the San Joaquin Valley from the Mojave Desert.

Tehama County.title: Tehama County
Tehama County.byline: Tehama County is in the Shasta Cascades region of California.

Tehran.title: Tehran
Tehran.byline: Tehran (also spelled Teheran) (Persian: تهران), is the capital city of Iran.

Tehuacán.title: Tehuacán
Tehuacán.byline: Tehuacán is a good-size city of almost 300,000 people (2020) in Puebla (state).
